  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized placebo-controlled study with vitamine K2 (Menaquinone-4) in calcified carotid
      stenosis. We evaluate the plaque remodelling after administration of vitamine, reducing the
      calcified component.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
